  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase I, open-label, multi-centre study designed to assess the safety and
      tolerability of Cediranib in combination with lomustine in patients with primary recurrent
      malignant brain tumour.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
